text: Neeco Delaf is a French music producer and songwriter. Delaf produces mainly downtempo, chillout electronic music with influences of pop and trip hop. In 2016 his song "Anthropology" was compiled in Café del Mar's album "Café del Mar, Vol. 22". == Discography == === EP/singles === * 2017: In The Night EP *# Banque *# If You Let Me (feat.
